ede95630a005e626a043d455b400c31483e72ec","tid":473270,"uid":46807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T09:37:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點會買orange儲值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上台啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主只去3個月 點上台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有住址 有Credit Card就上得㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平上面300幾蚊嗰啲成倍喎<br />\n走嘅時候記得cut card咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來可以咁!<br />\n樓主, 可唔可以分享多D...<br />\n例如 咩台?咩鋪頭黎?<br />\nThanks!"},{"pid":"dd93b2c14b0f9ac94a534ccedef94285f04addcc","tid":473270,"uid":46807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T09:37:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係英國用3 &pound;20 12GB feel at home 歐洲都用得</blockquote><br />\n法國可以買到嗎??"},{"pid":"8a41fe3dfbec86726259f5569c5af88c1d2fb3b9","tid":473270,"uid":46807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T09:38:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去到當地買wifi hotspot Plan</blockquote><br />\nHi 巴打, 想請問下可以係咩鋪頭買wifi hotspot???<br />\nThanks"},{"pid":"115e6e6f27c032904f00dec14b6c6309c99ce449","tid":473270,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T15:10:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去到當地買wifi hotspot Plan</blockquote><br />\nHi 巴打, 想請問下可以係咩鋪頭買wifi hotspot???<br />\nThanks</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n通常都係個幾間,orange 最快最貴<br />\n唔係wifi蛋, 係佢地街上面既wifi熱點<br />\n你check 下佢cover 邊度先,同埋你平日多數去邊<br />\n<br />\n建議買Lycamoblie同黎text+普通上網,睇YouTube就連wifi 熱點<br />\n<br />\nBtw,係街上面比錢買既wifi好撚快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇計,係咁煩麻,除非你比得起10歐1gb top-up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3295519a96d03cd1ba84370e3e5a3dbd64247b54","tid":473270,"uid":46807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T04:11:28.000Z","msg":"多謝咁多位ching！<br />\n最後我去左free上台，20歐1個月，有50gb data.<br />\n加上免費打電話返黎hk，歐盟哥以免費漫遊...<br />\n好抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但接收有d差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}